### API Routers

#### [NEW] [routers/scan.py](file:///c:/Users/kunal/Desktop/OpenLabel/routers/scan.py)

**`POST /api/v1/scan/image`** — The primary endpoint Member 1 calls
1. Receives base64-encoded image from Flutter app
2. Sends image directly to Gemini 2.0 Flash with the Tech-Justice system prompt
3. Receives structured JSON analysis
4. Stores scan record in `scans` table
5. Returns the full report to Flutter

**`POST /api/v1/scan/link`** — Alternative input via product URL
1. Receives product URL (BigBasket, Blinkit, Amazon, Flipkart, etc.)
2. Calls `scraper.py` to extract product text data
3. Enriches with OSINT wholesale price data from `osint_data.py`
4. Pipes enriched text to Gemini AI engine
5. Stores + returns report

#### [NEW] [routers/reports.py](file:///c:/Users/kunal/Desktop/OpenLabel/routers/reports.py)

**`GET /api/v1/reports`** — Authenticated user's scan history
- Paginated list of past scans with trust scores
- Sorted by most recent

**`GET /api/v1/reports/{scan_id}`** — Full report detail
- Returns complete JSON report for a specific scan

#### [NEW] [routers/users.py](file:///c:/Users/kunal/Desktop/OpenLabel/routers/users.py)

**`GET /api/v1/profile`** — Get user's allergy/preference profile
**`PUT /api/v1/profile`** — Update allergies & preference level

