- Used by the "Economic Sniper" feature to flag below-wholesale retail prices

#### [NEW] [data/wholesale_prices.json](file:///c:/Users/kunal/Desktop/OpenLabel/data/wholesale_prices.json)
Static JSON with Indian wholesale commodity prices in INR/kg:
- Honey, Ghee, Olive Oil, Saffron, Coconut Oil, A2 Milk, etc.
